I have been going to Dr. Neeraja Patcha since my baby was born and all vaccinations has been done here.. she is very friendly and the environment of the hospital is clean and most mportantly limited people and limited appointments not crowded at all as in other places..I feel it's safe place during these pandemic situation.. I am writing this review after 1 year and 2 months and highly recommend Dr. Neeraja if you looking for pediatrician for your child... She makes children feel happy by talking sweetly and giving stickers....she hears all the health issues slowly and gives us a positive attitude towards our kids health...
